quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,68,mein tumhe khuda ke pegham pohanchata hon aur tumhara amanat daar khair khwah hon
  7,69,kiya tum ko is baat se taajjub howa hai ke tum mein se 1 shakhs ke haath tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas nasiyaat aayi taakay woh tumhe dry aur yaad karo to karo jab is ne tum ko qoum Nooh ke baad sardar banaya. aur tum ko phelao ziyada diya. pas khuda ki nematon ko yaad karo. taakay nijaat haasil karo
  7,70,woh kehnay lagey ke tum hamaray paas is liye aeye ho ke hum akailey khuda hi ki ibadat karen. aur jin ko hamaray baap dada pujte chalay aeye hain un ko chore den? to agar sachey ho to jis cheez se hamein darate ho usay le aao
  7,71,Hood ne kaha tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par azaab aur ghazab ka ( nazil hona ) muqarrar ho chuka hai.kiya tum mujh se aisay naamon ke baray mein jhagarte ho jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne ( apni taraf se ) rakh liye hain. jin ki khuda ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki. to tum bhi intzaar karo mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon
  7,72,phir hum ne Hood ko aur jo log un ke sath they un ko nijaat bakhsh aur jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya tha un ki jarr kaat di aur woh imaan laane walay they hi nahi
  7,73,aur qoum smod ki taraf un ke bhai Saleh ko bheja. ( to ) Saleh ne kaha ke ae qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se aik moujza aa chuka hai. ( yani ) yahi khuda ki oontni tumahray liye moujza hai. to usay ( azad ) chore do ke khuda ki zameen mein chrti phiray aur tum usay buri niyat se haath bhi nah lagana. warna azabِ alim mein tumhe pakar le ga
